%% Background-job tenant resolution. See 08-background-and-storage-isolation.md
flowchart TB
  Cron[cron / webhook fires] --> Auth[auth: CRON_SECRET / signature - fail closed]
  Auth --> Resolve[resolveBackgroundTenant kind, explicit?]
  Resolve --> Off{TENANCY_ENABLED?}
  Off -- false --> Ref[reference tenant jkiss - no key change]
  Off -- true --> Explicit{explicit tenant named?}
  Explicit -- no --> FailClosed[THROW + telemetry - background-tenant-resolution]
  Explicit -- yes --> Norm[normalizeTenantId]
  Ref --> Wrap[withBackgroundTenant -> runWithTenant]
  Norm --> Wrap
  Wrap --> Work[sweep/handler: redis keys scope to tenant]
